<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cmn-Hans">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Document</title>
<style>
/*原理：我们打个比方，有四块红色和黑色的木板代表元素的四个边框，把他们两横两竖重叠起来，这时候他们在二维平面的投影便成了上面的效果。*/
.triangle_border_nw{
    width:0;
    height:0;
    border-width:30px 30px 0 0;/*左边为0,被上边全部投影*/
    border-style:solid;
    border-color:#6c6 transparent transparent transparent;
    margin:40px auto;
    position:relative;
}
/*或者
.triangle_border_nw{
    width:0;
    height:0;
    border-width:0 0 30px 30px;
    border-style:solid;
    border-color:transparent transparent transparent #6c6;
    margin:40px auto;
    position:relative;
}*/
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="triangle_border_nw"></div>
</body>
</html>